2. Preview
	@ How do you make a dance move?
	You can create various motions by adjusting the angle and moving time of the 4 motors connected to the AsomeBot. You can create the motion to wag foot as follows:
	[image ./images/blocks/16-01.png]

	@ Create a new dance move
	You can use 3 methods to create new dance moves.
	1. First, combine existing motions into a single motion. This motion can be bundled together like a single motion
	[image ./images/blocks/16-02.png]
	2. Second, specify one servomotor angle and motion time at a time. You must specify which servomotor to move.
	[image ./images/blocks/16-03.png]
	3. Last, specify multiple servomotor angles and motion times at a time. Specify the angle and moving speed of each motor at a time.Creating a motion like the one below will create a motion that takes 2 seconds to lift and lower two feet.
	[image ./images/blocks/16-04.png]

	@ Adjusting moving time
	The moving time of the motor set to 1 second and 0.1 second will demonstrate completely different motions due to the difference of the moving speed even if the same motion is created as below.
	[image ./images/blocks/16-05.png]


