4. Play Activity
	@ Game Rule
	① Create a program that can control AsomeBot with the Asome Controller.
	② Create 3 new dance moves of your choice.
	- Motion created by combining existing motions
	- Motion created by moving the motor one by one
	- Motion created by moving multiple motors at once
	③ Create a program to execute the new motions with the number button of the Asome Controller.

	@ Algorithm
	Did you created awesome dance moves? Show off the dance moves you created with the method below:
	① Demonstrate your dance move and let the audience know the name of the dance move.
	② Also explain why you created the dance move.
	③ Listen to your friends’ dance move story.
	④Play the music and let the robot to perform awesome dance to the dance move you created.
